    "plainEnglish": "This code describes a mental health problem that is directly caused by a medical condition or physical illness affecting the brain, when that problem doesn't fit into more specific categories. For example, mood changes, anxiety, or behavioral issues that result from hormonal disorders, infections, or other medical conditions would be coded here. The key point is that your doctor has identified a physical/medical cause for your mental symptoms, rather than the symptoms being primary psychiatric conditions.",
