    "whoUses": "Addiction medicine specialists, psychiatrists, primary care doctors, and pain management specialists use this code when documenting a patient's recovery status. It commonly appears on EOB statements for patients receiving treatment at substance abuse clinics, counseling centers, or during follow-up visits with providers managing their recovery.",
