    "whoUses": "Addiction medicine specialists, psychiatrists, and mental health professionals use this code when treating patients with opioid use disorder who develop concurrent psychotic symptoms. This code appears on EOB statements less frequently than primary addiction diagnoses alone, as it requires documentation of both the opioid dependence and the specific psychotic manifestation by the treating provider.",
