    "plainEnglish": "This code describes a situation where someone is misusing cannabis and has developed a mental health condition involving delusions—false beliefs that feel completely real to them even though they're not grounded in reality. Cannabis use can trigger or worsen psychotic symptoms like delusions in some people, especially those with genetic vulnerability to psychosis. A patient might experience fixed false beliefs (for example, believing people are plotting against them) that occur in the context of their cannabis abuse.",
