    "whoUses": "Psychiatrists, addiction medicine specialists, primary care physicians, and substance abuse counselors use this code when evaluating patients with sedative or benzodiazepine misuse. It commonly appears on EOBs for mental health or addiction treatment visits, though patients often see the broader term 'substance abuse' or 'medication misuse' rather than this specific code.",
